"use strict";(self.webpackChunk_N_E=self.webpackChunk_N_E||[]).push([[118137],{118137:a=>{a.exports=JSON.parse('{"seo":{"title":"A hegycs\xfacs t\xfara a Hostel Brikette-től","description":"\xc9rje el Monte Sant\'Angel\xf3t, az Amalfi-part legmagasabb pontj\xe1t ezekkel az \xfatmutat\xe1sokkal, felk\xe9sz\xfcl\xe9si tippekkel \xe9s figyelmeztet\xe9sekkel."},"linkLabel":"T\xfara a hegy tetej\xe9n a Hostel Brikette-től","intro":["Monte Sant\'Angelo towers above the Amalfi Coast and rewards hikers with sweeping 360-degree views stretching from Capri to the Sorrentine Peninsula.","This itinerary starts from Hostel Brikette, guides you up to Santa Maria del Castello, and explains the final push to the summit so you know exactly what to expect before committing."],"sections":[{"id":"why-go","title":"Why tackle this hike","body":["Views from the summit sweep across the peninsula towards Capri and down the Lattari mountains, making the grind worthwhile for photographers and hikers alike.","Reaching the Amalfi Coast\'s highest point is a satisfying physical challenge and a story you will trade with other travellers back at the hostel.","The long ascent doubles as a serious cardio session, especially if you are training for bigger treks later in your trip."]},{"id":"getting-to-santa-maria","title":"Getting to Santa Maria del Castello","body":["Follow our standard hostel-to-Santa-Maria directions until you arrive in the village; that climb covers just over one third of the total elevation for the day.","Take a breather in the square, refill water if the bar is open, and check that everyone in your group still feels strong before committing to the exposed upper trail."]},{"id":"santa-maria-to-summit","title":"From Santa Maria to the summit","body":["From the crossroads at the top of the village, turn right up the paved lane until a junction, then turn left and continue past the restaurant until the road bends sharply left.","Leave the road on the right-hand side, following the side path that drops slightly between houses. It will feel like private property at first, but you are still on the right track.","Stay on the mountain trail for an extended stretch until you reach a signed crossroads. Ignore the downhill options and take the steeply rising path.","The ascent quickly zig-zags before easing into a long, flatter traverse along the left-hand side of the mountain face. When you spot stone-cut steps on your right, follow them around the back of the peak for the final push.","Those rock steps lead to the last ramp of the day—keep climbing and you will emerge on the summit plateau with panoramic views in every direction."]}],"essentialsTitle":"Essentials","essentials":["Szem\xe9lyenk\xe9nt legal\xe1bb 2 liter v\xedz plusz s\xf3s harapnival\xf3k; Santa Maria del Castello ut\xe1n nincs megb\xedzhat\xf3 ut\xe1nt\xf6lt\xe9s.","Massz\xedv t\xfaracipő markolattal – a felső \xf6sv\xe9ny szakaszai szikl\xe1sak, lazak \xe9s kil\xe1tszottak.","Napv\xe9delem \xe9s r\xe9tegek a cs\xfacsra; a sz\xe9l m\xe9g meleg napokon is \xe1tcsaphat a gerincen."],"typicalCostsTitle":"Typical costs","typicalCosts":["A t\xfara\xfatvonal ingyenes; k\xf6lts\xe9gvet\xe9se 5–10 eur\xf3, ha azt tervezi, hogy megjutalmazza mag\xe1t egy itallal vagy harapnival\xf3val a Santa Maria del Castell\xf3ban.","Ha \xfagy d\xf6nt, hogy egy m\xe1sik falun kereszt\xfcl ereszkedik le, ahelyett, hogy visszafel\xe9 gyalogolna, adja vissza a SITA buszjegyeit vagy a komp viteld\xedjait."],"tipsTitle":"Smart timing","tips":["Ny\xe1ron hajnalban kezdje, hogy elker\xfclje a cs\xfacshő alatti m\xe1sz\xe1st; a k\xe9ső őszi \xe9s tavaszi d\xe9lut\xe1nok l\xe1gyabb f\xe9nyt k\xedn\xe1lnak tűző nap n\xe9lk\xfcl.","Ellenőrizze a vihar-előrejelz\xe9st – a felhőtakar\xf3 elt\xf6r\xf6lheti a kil\xe1t\xe1st, a nedves szikla pedig cs\xfasz\xf3ss\xe1 teszi a cs\xfacs l\xe9pcsőit.","T\xe1j\xe9koztassa valaki a hostelben a terv\xe9t \xe9s a v\xe1rhat\xf3 visszat\xe9r\xe9si idej\xe9t, mielőtt elindulna."],"warningsTitle":"When to reconsider","warnings":["Hagyja ki a t\xfar\xe1t, ha nem rendelkezik hegyi tapasztalattal vagy erős erőnl\xe9ttel; a tart\xf3s szintemelked\xe9s b\xfcntető, \xe9s kev\xe9s a mentőpont.","Ker\xfclje el az \xfatvonalat, ha a magass\xe1gok nyugtalan\xedtanak – a szabadd\xe1 v\xe1lt p\xe1rk\xe1nyok \xe9s meredek es\xe9sek m\xe9g a magabiztos t\xfar\xe1z\xf3kat is kih\xedv\xe1s el\xe9 \xe1ll\xedtj\xe1k.","Ne pr\xf3b\xe1lja meg feljutni a cs\xfacsra a cs\xfacs ny\xe1ri d\xe9lut\xe1nokon, amikor a hős\xe9g \xe9s az extra v\xedz sz\xe1ll\xedt\xe1s\xe1nak sz\xfcks\xe9gess\xe9ge fokozza a fesz\xfclts\xe9get."],"steps":[{"name":"Climb to Santa Maria del Castello","text":"Haszn\xe1lja a sz\xe1ll\xf3 Santa Maria del Castello fel\xe9 vezető \xfatvonal\xe1t; a t\xe9r el\xe9r\xe9se azt jelenti, hogy a magass\xe1g nagyj\xe1b\xf3l egyharmad\xe1t teljes\xedtette."},{"name":"Join the mountain trail","text":"A falu kereszteződ\xe9s\xe9től jobbra, majd balra az \xe9tterem mellett, \xe9s hagyja el az utat a h\xe1zakat k\xf6r\xfclvevő jobb oldali \xfaton."},{"name":"Commit to the upper ascent","text":"K\xf6vesse a zord \xf6sv\xe9nyt a jelzett kereszteződ\xe9shez, \xe9s v\xe1lassza ki azt az utat, amely egyenesen felfel\xe9 tart a cs\xfacs fel\xe9."},{"name":"Navigate the zig-zags","text":"Hajtson \xe1t meredek v\xe1lt\xe1sokon, am\xedg az \xf6sv\xe9ny ellaposodik a hegy bal oldal\xe1n."},{"name":"Take the rock-cut stairs","text":"M\xe1ssz fel a jobb oldali kől\xe9pcsők\xf6n, a hegyoldal m\xf6g\xe9 hurkolva az utols\xf3 r\xe1mpa fel\xe9."},{"name":"Reach the summit","text":"K\xf6vesse az utols\xf3 emelkedőt a cs\xfacsra, \xe9s \xe9lvezze a panor\xe1m\xe1t, mielőtt visszamenne a Santa Maria fel\xe9."}],"faqsTitle":"FAQs","faqs":[{"q":"How long does the full hike take?","a":["Hagyjon 6–7 \xf3r\xe1t az oda-vissza \xfatra a Hostel Brikette-től, bele\xe9rtve a Santa Maria-i sz\xfcneteket \xe9s a cs\xfacson elt\xf6lt\xf6tt időt."]},{"q":"Is the trail marked?","a":["A jelzők ritk\xe1k a Santa Mari\xe1n t\xfal; vigyen mag\xe1val egy offline t\xe9rk\xe9pet, \xe9s figyeljen a nyilv\xe1nval\xf3an kopott \xf6sv\xe9nyekre \xe9s a csom\xf3pontokn\xe1l l\xe9vő \xfatjelző t\xe1bl\xe1kra."]},{"q":"Can I turn back early?","a":["Igen. Ha a felső r\xe9sz t\xfals\xe1gosan kitettnek tűnik, \xe9lvezze a kil\xe1t\xe1st a Santa Maria-b\xf3l vagy az als\xf3 \xe1tj\xe1r\xf3kb\xf3l, \xe9s t\xe9rjen vissza arra az \xfatra, ahol j\xf6tt."]}],"toc":{"labels":{"warnings":"When to reconsider"}},"gallery":{"title":"Fot\xf3gal\xe9ria","items":[{"alt":"Looking across the peninsula to Capri","caption":"Kil\xe1t\xe1s a f\xe9lszigeten \xe1t Caprira"},{"alt":"Scan to Share QR code","caption":"Oszd meg, olvasd be a QR-k\xf3dot"},{"alt":"Trail near the summit","caption":"A cs\xfacs k\xf6zel\xe9ben"}]}}')}}]);